There are general set of 10 codes that recommended and published for people listing to emergency services radio bands as a go by.  Many departments customize the 10 codes for their department, so from location to location the codes don&#39;t always mean the same thing.  When multiple departments are working together Home Land Security recommends that to eliminate possible misunderstandings, 10 codes should not be used.


Regards,
Jon in Texas





